name: TrendingHashtags
0:
”Alexa, open trending hashtags”
”Alexa, launch trending hashtags”
”Alexa, ask trending hashtags what is trending in India”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: trending hashtags
des:
This skill gives you, twitter trending topics in your country. You can also ask for other countries twitter trends as well. 
To get started for trending hashtags, just ask Alexa:
"Alexa, open trending hashtags"
Then respond to Alexa, with your country name like "India"
Note: As of now, we are not supporting local language trending hashtags topics.
